product.title: Cute Coral Octopus Part-Cotton Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Looking for some comfy pieces?

    Add some softness and sweetness to your life with this hoodie. Featuring a cute, adorable, coral octopus floating on the front of your hoodie. Style this with any bottoms and fresh kicks to complete the look.

    Choose between 12 different colors. We always recommend choosing 1 size up giving you the oversized hoodie look.

    Get ready to give your look a kawaii-style with this hoodie!

    Unique and stylish design that will make you look super cute. Made from premium quality polyester mixed with pure cotton, making it feel super soft on the skin. A comfortable overlay for everyday wear.

    Available in five different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below.

    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 41 43 45 47 48
    Length 23 24 25 26 27
    Sleeve 20 20 20 21 21
               
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 107 111 115 119 123
    Length 60 62 64 66 68
    Sleeve 50 51 52 53 54


    Features

    😍 Made from 70% premium polyester and 30% pure cotton
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability
    😍 Coral Octopus Print on front only

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.


  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
